{"tid":802960,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【業主鬥劈】得寶「鳳凰樓」劈價一成 跌穿5球易手","createTime":"2018-09-01T23:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:23:51.000Z","uid":147097,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0631e434539edf7592cc8bec721fbfee104c1553","tid":802960,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:40:02.000Z","msg":"細價樓出現劈價潮，九龍灣得寶花園重現「4字頭」成交。消息指F座極高層3室「鳳凰樓」(頂樓對落一層)，實用面積282方呎，屬一房間隔，<span style=\"color: red;\">剛僅以485萬元易手，呎價17,199元，低市價逾一成。此單位獲中銀及滙豐銀行估值573萬及542萬元</span>，是次成交較估值低最多88萬元或15%。代理透露，單位於市場放盤已有一個月，原叫價530萬元，一直乏人問津，加上業主已移民及希望套現，不惜劈價求售。<br />\n<br />\n中原成交紀錄顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">得寶花園A座高層3室，實用面積282方呎，上月以560萬元成交</span>，呎價19,858元。<br />\n<br />\n得寶花園本月只錄得兩宗買賣，除上述成交外，另一宗為D座低層6室，<span style=\"color: red;\">實用面積同為282方呎，以520萬元沽出</span>，呎價18,440元。今次賣出的「鳳凰樓」竟比低層戶平6.7%。 <br />\n<br />\n一個月跌成75萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2856ea3f0cab3afb60cf4769cddc7b8f0c54a4a1","tid":802960,"uid":108201,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:44:30.000Z","msg":"代買左樓既樓豬答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/074428_9383ba7e9f8773a065868ae30c89ec73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F074428_9383ba7e9f8773a065868ae30c89ec73.png&h=9a3972a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e25ff72a7cc6c8d139d653fdd01c9726d4bceaee","tid":802960,"uid":52911,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:45:07.000Z","msg":"樓爆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n等多半年300萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849ae7a110efb97d2ea0fd6b64a2a27ac8036cf0","tid":802960,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"淡淡咪又係買唔起"},{"pid":"4075c2f19a04149ea9844c41780e7ae9791b4945"